    },
    {
      "content": [
        {
          "content": "servant",
          "type": "text",
        },
      ],
      "marker": "bd",
      "type": "character",
    },
    {
      "content": " of God and an ",
      "type": "text",
    },
    {
      "content": [
        {
          "content": "apostle",
          "type": "text",
        },
      ],
      "marker": "bd",
      "type": "character",
    },
    {
      "content": " of Jesus Christ, for the faith of God's chosen people and the knowledge of the truth. ",
      "type": "text",
    },
    {
      "content": [
        {
          "content": "2",
          "type": "text",
        },
      ],
      "marker": "v",
      "type": "character",
    },
    {
      "content": "These are in hope of eternal life that God, who does not lie, ",
      "type": "text",
    },
    {
      "content": [
        {
          "content": "promised",
          "type": "text",
        },
      ],
      "marker": "add",
      "type": "character",
    },
    {
      "content": " before all the ages of time. ",
      "type": "text",
    },
    {
      "content": [
        {
          "content": "3",
          "type": "text",
        },
      ],
      "marker": "v",
      "type": "character",
    },
    {
      "content": "At the right time, he revealed his word by the message that he trusted me to deliver by the command of God our Savior.",
      "type": "text",
    },
  ],
  "marker": "p",
  "type": "paragraph",
}
