      {
        "content": [
          {
            "content": "5",
            "type": "text",
          },
        ],
        "marker": "v",
        "type": "character",
      },
      {
        "content": "For this purpose I left you in Crete, that you might set in order things not yet complete and ordain elders in every city as I directed you— ",
        "type": "text",
      },
      {
        "content": [
          {
            "content": "6",
            "type": "text",
          },
        ],
        "marker": "v",
        "type": "character",
      },
      {
        "content": "if anyone is blameless, ",
        "type": "text",
      },
      {
        "attributes": {
          "strong": "G3588",
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "content": "the",
            "type": "text",
          },
        ],
        "marker": "w",
        "type": "character",
      },
      {
        "content": " husband of one wife, having faithful children not accused of reckless behavior or rebellion.",
        "type": "text",
      },
    ],
    "marker": "p",
    "type": "paragraph",
  },
  {
    "content": [
      {
        "content": [
          {
            "content": "7",
            "type": "text",
          },
        ],
        "marker": "v",
        "type": "character",
      },
      {
        "content": "For the overseer must be blameless, as God's household manager.",
        "type": "text",
      },
    ],
    "marker": "q1",
    "type": "paragraph",
  },
  {
    "content": [
      {
        "content": "He must not be arrogant,",
        "type": "text",
      },
    ],
    "marker": "q2",
    "type": "paragraph",
  },
  {
    "content": [
      {
        "content": "not easily angered,",
