    "marker": "li1",
    "type": "paragraph",
  },
  {
    "content": [
      {
        "content": "holy,",
        "type": "text",
      },
    ],
    "marker": "li1",
    "type": "paragraph",
  },
  {
    "content": [
      {
        "content": "and self-controlled.",
        "type": "text",
      },
    ],
    "marker": "li1",
    "type": "paragraph",
  },
  {
    "content": [
      {
        "content": [
          {
            "content": "9",
            "type": "text",
          },
        ],
        "marker": "v",
        "type": "character",
      },
      {
        "content": "He should hold tightly to the trustworthy message that was taught, so that he may be able both to encourage others with sound ",
        "type": "text",
      },
      {
        "content": [
          {
            "content": "doctrine",
            "type": "text",
          },
        ],
        "marker": "nd",
        "type": "character",
      },
      {
        "content": " ",
        "type": "text",
      },
      {
        "caller": "+",
        "content": [
          {
            "content": [
              {
                "content": "1:9 ",
                "type": "text",
              },
            ],
            "marker": "fr",
            "type": "character",
          },
          {
            "content": [
              {
                "content": "sound doctrine ",
                "type": "text",
              },
            ],
            "marker": "fq",
            "type": "character",
          },
          {
            "content": [
              {
                "content": "This is a metaphor that means "correct teaching" or "true teaching."",
                "type": "text",
              },
            ],
            "marker": "ft",
            "type": "character",
          },
        ],
        "marker": "f",
        "type": "note",
      },
      {
        "content": " and to correct those who oppose him.",
        "type": "text",
      },
    ],
    "marker": "p",
    "type": "paragraph",
  },
  {
    "content": [],
    "marker": "s5",
    "type": "paragraph",
  },
  {
    "content": [
      {
        "content": [
          {
            "content": "10",
            "type": "text",
          },
        ],
        "marker": "v",
        "type": "character",
      },
      {
        "content": "For there are many rebellious people, empty talkers, and deceivers, especially those of the circumcision. ",
        "type": "text",
      },
      {
        "content": [
          {
            "content": "11",
            "type": "text",
          },
        ],
        "marker": "v",
        "type": "character",
      },
      {
        "content": "It is necessary to stop them. They are upsetting whole families by teaching for shameful profit what they should not teach.",
        "type": "text",
      },
    ],
